<P>The Highwayman&mdash;The Star and Garter&mdash;Origin of Hoops&mdash;The Waggon Rut&mdash;Travelling Picquet&mdash;The poor Seaman&mdash;Wind&s;or Terrace&mdash;The Departure&mdash;Lord Praetor's electioneering Expedition&mdash;The Meeting&mdash;The old Maid and old Soldier&mdash;Chit Chat&mdash;Story of Count O'Reily&mdash;Aquatic Sport of Swan Hopping&mdash;Tri&s;tram Shandy&mdash;Story of Count O'Dunn, and the Queen of Portugal&mdash;<HI>Un petit Souper</HI>&mdash;The <HI>Illu&s;tration</HI> by an Extingui&s;her, &amp;c.</P>
